    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/villa-alessandra-hotel/hotel/paris-fr.html",
    "name": "Villa Alessandra Hotel",
    "detail": "I've been staying at this hotel when in Paris for about the past 10 years or so. The location is excellent, close to shops, good restaurants, public transport and the Marche Poncelet. It's in a quiet little square, so there is no traffic noise. Value for money, given Paris hotel prices, is excellent. As a long time regular client, the staff all recognize me and I tend to get a little spoiled which is nice. The star rating is actually given by the government not the hotel itself, if it was elsewhere I would call it a 3 star, it's simple, without pretention and you'd really have a difficult time finding a better deal in Paris when you take into account where it is and what the prices are like. ",
